flowchart TD
  Controller[Controller<br/>HTTP binding only]
  Service[Service<br/>Use-case orchestration and domain decisions]
  Repository[Repository<br/>Prisma query shape and data access]
  Prisma[PrismaService<br/>Client lifecycle and DB adapter]
  Database[(PostgreSQL<br/>Durable relational data)]

  Controller --> Service --> Repository --> Prisma --> Database

  Controller -. why .-> CWhy[Prevents HTTP concerns from leaking into business logic]
  Service -. why .-> SWhy[Keeps workflows testable and transaction boundaries explicit]
  Repository -. why .-> RWhy[Makes query performance user scoping and indexes reviewable]
  Prisma -. why .-> PWhy[Single database abstraction and generated schema types]
  Database -. why .-> DWhy[ACID persistence for financial records]
